OBJECTIVE: Assessing the cost of subsidizing access to household natural gas 
(HNG) and its impact on the health of about 35,000 poor households 
(socioeconomic strata 1 and 2) in Colombia, sponsored by a Global Partnership on 
Output-Based Aid (GPOBA) project.
